562
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:44,330
Come on, come on, come on.

563
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:46,410
Come on, come on, come on.

564
00:38:46,440 --> 00:38:47,000
Come on...

565
00:39:06,680 --> 00:39:07,480
