575
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:37,160
But it's a good start.

576
00:39:39,380 --> 00:39:41,160
At least, I got to hug them.

577
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:43,040
This time around,

578
00:39:43,380 --> 00:39:46,240
I really felt like Mom and Dad were there.

579
00:40:04,600 --> 00:40:05,280
Duang.

580
00:40:08,420 --> 00:40:09,160
Thank you.

581
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:14,320
