589
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:11,560
Sweet dreams, Duang.

590
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:17,520
Sweet dreams.

591
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:32,400
Duang?

592
00:41:33,120 --> 00:41:33,760
Hm?

593
