I'm not.

604
00:42:38,380 --> 00:42:39,320
Just browsing.

605
00:42:40,720 --> 00:42:42,120
Do you think
the photos would come out beautiful?

606
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:43,370
Of course,

607
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:44,360
look at what a pro we are.

608
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:45,720
Nothing compares to your beauty, though,

609
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:47,250
pretty.

610
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:54,360
Wanna go for a walk?

611
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:56,120
Then we can come back for the photos.

612
00:43:15,720 --> 00:43:19,840
♫I'm not leaving soon, so bear with me♫

613
00:43:20,440 --> 00:43:24,920
♫Wherever you are is where I'll always be♫

614
00:43:25,160 --> 00:43:28,990
♫Wherever you go, I'll find you eventually♫

615
00:43:29,020 --> 00:43:31,290
♫You may push me away, but I won't flee♫

616
00:43:31,320 --> 00:43:34,250
♫Who would you love if it weren't me?♫

617
00:43:34,280 --> 00:43:36,560
♫So, wanna make a deal, maybe?♫

618
00:43:36,620 --> 00:43:38,990
♫Alright, alright, don't worry♫

619
00:43:39,020 --> 00:43:41,020
♫I know you're also into me,♫

620
00:43:41,050 --> 00:43:43,960
♫Don't you feel the same? I can see♫

621
00:43:44,720 --> 00:43:50,110
♫I'll keep on flirting, don't try to avoid me♫

622
00:43:50,140 --> 00:43:54,810
♫'Cause I won't stop till you fall for me♫

623
00:43:54,840 --> 00:43:59,530
♫I'll keep on flirting, I won't stop, I guarantee♫

624
00:43:59,560 --> 00:44:06,040
♫I'll love you hard,
and once you say yes, I'll set you free♫

625
00:44:12,960 --> 00:44:18,880
♫I'll keep flirting with you nonstop♫

626
00:44:23,560 --> 00:44:24,240
Hey, you.

627
00:44:24,500 --> 00:44:25,210
Hm?

628
00:44:25,240 --> 00:44:26,480
Let's change our outfits.

629
