635
00:45:28,480 --> 00:45:30,760
Don't rush to say I'm not a hottie.

636
00:45:31,180 --> 00:45:33,320
Just give me a chance to dress up first.

637
00:45:33,350 --> 00:45:34,930
If you see me when I'm not mewing,

638
00:45:34,960 --> 00:45:36,360
I'm gonna look skibidi.

639
00:45:36,980 --> 00:45:37,920
Speak proper language.

640
00:45:38,520 --> 00:45:39,120
What?

641
