Why, though?

642
00:45:41,260 --> 00:45:43,240
I think I look fine in this.

643
00:45:43,500 --> 00:45:44,640
Plus, it's not expensive.

644
00:45:45,280 --> 00:45:46,040
It is.

645
00:45:46,320 --> 00:45:47,770
Whoa...

646
00:45:47,800 --> 00:45:49,840
Said the boy
who wears shoes worth 30,000 baht.

647
00:45:50,020 --> 00:45:51,440
Isn't it a bit rich coming from you?

648
00:45:52,960 --> 00:45:55,510
Said the boy
who bought a camera worth 55,000 baht

649
00:45:55,540 --> 00:45:57,040
and ended up having no money to eat?

650
00:45:57,600 --> 00:45:58,450
Isn't it a bit rich?

651
00:45:59,920 --> 00:46:00,560
Then...

652
00:46:01,560 --> 00:46:02,960
give me a reason.

653
00:46:03,460 --> 00:46:05,200
If it sounds reasonable, I won't buy it.

654
00:46:09,840 --> 00:46:10,440
Why?

655
00:46:10,940 --> 00:46:13,400
I look good in darker colors, don't I?

656
00:46:13,720 --> 00:46:14,680
Just buy it, then.

657
00:46:16,320 --> 00:46:17,920
Just say you're possessive.

658
00:46:27,080 --> 00:46:27,760
How about...

659
00:46:29,180 --> 00:46:30,200
