I'm teasing you?

667
00:48:05,880 --> 00:48:06,880
Bastard.

668
00:48:26,840 --> 00:48:28,600
Your heart is beating out of your chest.

669
00:48:30,940 --> 00:48:32,700
Now you're the one

670
00:48:33,300 --> 00:48:34,080
