674
00:49:02,740 --> 00:49:03,360
In your dream.

675
00:49:04,100 --> 00:49:05,040
Go out and pay.

676
00:49:16,880 --> 00:49:18,480
Mm, I got everything I need.

677
00:49:23,380 --> 00:49:24,000
What?

678
00:49:25,820 --> 00:49:27,520
I want to invite you over for a meal.

679
00:49:28,180 --> 00:49:29,200
Do you wanna come?

680
00:49:29,820 --> 00:49:31,000
Why bring this up all of a sudden?

681
00:49:31,640 --> 00:49:33,760
Well, when I was shopping earlier,

682
00:49:34,300 --> 00:49:36,560
I realized
I haven't introduced you to Mami and Dad.

683
00:49:37,520 --> 00:49:39,000
What are you introducing me as?

684
00:49:40,120 --> 00:49:41,240
I'll tell them that

685
00:49:41,340 --> 00:49:42,600
you're my boyfriend.

686
00:49:44,400 --> 00:49:45,120
Is it a good idea?

687
00:49:45,500 --> 00:49:46,240
Mm.

688
00:49:47,500 --> 00:49:49,570
Dad and Mami are really nice.

689
00:49:49,600 --> 00:49:51,320
Mami is also good at making desserts.

690
00:49:54,680 --> 00:49:55,440
Please come.

691
00:49:57,240 --> 00:49:58,120
I don't mind.

692
00:49:58,260 --> 00:49:58,960
I can join.

693
00:49:59,440 --> 00:50:00,280
Then...

694
00:50:00,310 --> 00:50:02,160
Let's go see your mom and dad today,

695
00:50:02,360 --> 00:50:03,480
and we'll visit my house later.

696
00:50:04,080 --> 00:50:04,840
Mm.

697
00:50:05,440 --> 00:50:06,120
Let's go.

698
00:50:11,440 --> 00:50:12,850
- Hey, let's take a photo.
- Hm?

699
00:50:12,880 --> 00:50:13,280
Mm.

700
00:50:23,480 --> 00:50:24,530
Look at how cute you are.

701
00:50:24,560 --> 00:50:25,720
What do you want, baby?

702
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:29,700
Duang.

703
00:50:39,320 --> 00:50:40,120
Ow!

704
00:50:42,160 --> 00:50:43,760
Here you go.

705
00:50:43,790 --> 00:50:45,770
- Here's yours, sweetie.
- Alright, thank you, honey.

706
00:50:45,800 --> 00:50:46,810
- Here's yours, kids.
- Popcorn!

707
00:50:46,840 --> 00:50:48,600
- Thank you, Mom.
- Thank you.

708
00:50:49,440 --> 00:50:51,080
- Where are we now?
- Oh, right.

709
00:50:51,600 --> 00:50:53,870
How about we start it over?

710
00:50:53,900 --> 00:50:54,920
This way, Mom can catch up, too.

711
00:50:55,020 --> 00:50:56,060
- Sure.
- Mm...

712
00:50:57,120 --> 00:50:57,880
