713
00:50:58,180 --> 00:50:59,000
Actually,

714
00:50:59,280 --> 00:51:00,600
I got lost many times with the subtitles.

715
00:51:02,400 --> 00:51:03,590
Alright, then. Let's start over.

716
00:51:03,620 --> 00:51:06,600
Okay! How nice it is
to watch a movie with Qin.

717
00:51:10,040 --> 00:51:10,680
Uh...

718
00:51:11,160 --> 00:51:12,080
Dad, Mom,

719
00:51:12,740 --> 00:51:15,840
I have...something to tell you.

720
00:51:17,580 --> 00:51:18,300
What is it, son?

721
00:51:23,200 --> 00:51:24,520
Duang and I...

722
00:51:29,880 --> 00:51:31,240
are boyfriends.

723
00:51:36,020 --> 00:51:37,160
Dad and I...

724
00:51:45,740 --> 00:51:48,240
Dad and I already knew.

725
00:51:49,840 --> 00:51:51,360
I'm so happy.

726
00:51:52,720 --> 00:51:54,680
Duang, come give Mom a hug.

727
00:51:58,360 --> 00:51:59,360
Then,

728
00:52:00,260 --> 00:52:02,120
I'll have to be serious.

729
00:52:06,800 --> 00:52:08,640
Welcome to the family, Duang.

730
00:52:08,780 --> 00:52:11,840
Yay!

731
00:52:11,920 --> 00:52:14,320
Yay!!

732
00:52:14,640 --> 00:52:16,970
Okay, I think
we'll need to start over again.

733
00:52:17,000 --> 00:52:18,320
Oh, that's right.

734
00:52:18,600 --> 00:52:20,250
This time, I'll make sure
to catch up with the subtitles.

735
00:52:20,280 --> 00:52:21,330
Get 'em, Duang.

736
00:52:21,360 --> 00:52:22,170
Sure thing.

737
00:52:22,200 --> 00:52:23,040
Ready?

738
00:52:24,100 --> 00:52:25,040
Let's go.

739
00:52:37,220 --> 00:52:38,120
Baby,

740
00:52:38,440 --> 00:52:39,440
come lie on my lap.

741
00:52:48,840 --> 00:52:49,920
Are you tired today?

742
00:52:53,560 --> 00:52:55,280
When you told Dad and Mom,

743
00:52:55,420 --> 00:52:56,720
I was flabbergasted.

744
00:52:56,720 --> 00:52:58,080
You really went all out.

745
00:52:58,960 --> 00:53:00,480
It gave me peace of mind
now that I've told them.

746
00:53:00,700 --> 00:53:01,360
How about you?

747
00:53:03,080 --> 00:53:04,080
I'm happy.

748
00:53:04,360 --> 00:53:05,640
I wanna eat you up!

749
00:53:09,720 --> 00:53:10,720
You're getting on my nerves.

750
00:53:12,080 --> 00:53:14,200
I want to thank you a million times more

751
00:53:14,200 --> 00:53:15,240
for choosing me.

752
00:53:16,140 --> 00:53:16,900
Stop.

753
00:53:25,300 --> 00:53:26,480
Didn't you see something?

754
00:53:26,900 --> 00:53:27,460
Hm?

755
00:53:27,740 --> 00:53:28,520
See what?

756
00:53:30,460 --> 00:53:32,100
When you were lifting the stuff up here,

757
00:53:32,420 --> 00:53:33,400
didn't you see anything?

758
00:53:36,260 --> 00:53:37,260
What?

759
00:53:41,520 --> 00:53:42,360
Is it...

760
00:53:42,900 --> 00:53:43,840
